rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"係易家咁既時勢黎講同fg <br />\n人工高過出面請少少<br />\n剩係星期一至五<br />\n返工時間算自由，但放工時間就唔定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"有冇20k?<br />\n會唔會加人工？"},{"pid":"c6004e75bba165086d433bde4286097bcb08abdb","tid":2462471,"uid":220804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37f7d31d52220c1d67ad93c2bf03af6a2a6987a0","tid":2462471,"uid":151065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T19:00:21.000Z","msg":"係咪兩年死約？<br />\n我見JobsDB有 諗緊做唔做<br />\n你會唔會想之後讀mphil?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0799e83a2a9a1e72c04c43ef3c5134996f0a5b","tid":2462471,"uid":220804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e021def60ffeaa9f2ea5d7385f0ddc4ce43fea3","tid":2462471,"uid":218729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f395fcd1c5fbba6712887ce9bb6c43ecb6ddc2b","tid":2462471,"uid":220804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"今年fg，好好彩識人介紹跟左個prof做RA<br />\n初時做都好地地，咁同時有人lead住，可能會有種安心啲感覺。<br />\n做左無耐左後，prof就開始比左個新project我做，要自己諗新idea，design實驗，寫下paper<br />\n已經成4、5個月，都好似唔係好做得出啲野，成個人完全諗唔到野，試左好多野都唔成功，又諗唔到新idea，之後就卡死左，更何況寫paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到啲同事好做到啲野出黎，相反自己就坐到個腦都塞L埋，好挫敗<br />\n成日好驚令prof好失望，唔知點交代，壓力好大，開始諗自己仲適唔適合呢個位，又驚比人炒搵唔到工，因為唔算啲咩專科，但我屋企仲對我好大期望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無助個陣就真係辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多謝大家睇完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n果種感覺好辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"共勉之啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到啲巴絲打都好好"}]}